      "text": "every person you add you can customize stuff\n(which friend, ai level, name, whatever)\n\nthen click on invite to actually send that to the\nserver and invite them.\n\nclick on plus to undo invite\n\nyou can change top stuff the entire time, its sent\nto the server once game starts",
